  "title": "EMMP Engineer (Woodlands)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Coordinate with EMMP Specialist Consultant, Nparks, PUB and other relevant Authorities</li>\n  <li>Oversee site activities to ensure compliance with environmental regulations and standards</li>\n  <li>Prepare technical reports and documentation based on monitoring data</li>\n  <li>Prepare EIA Report for Reclamation Project</li>\n  <li>Liasing with client, consultant and subcontractor</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree or Diploma holder in Civil Engineering</li>\n  <li>Prefarable 3 years experience in Marine / Land Civil Project in Singapore</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270 </p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R22110981</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Name: Law Mei Fong</p>",
